author: Sophie Scott And Nick Sas
title: Coronavirus data modelling has Australia in good position, but COVID-19 'here to stay'
description: The experts behind some of the modelling used to determine Australia's coronavirus response say Australia is in a "lucky" position, but warn the virus will remain part of everyday life.
